    "description": "这个游戏反映了现实生活，你必须经历如此多的失败才能取得成功，完成任务，并到达目标尽头的“喜悦”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/8e34a285516c53d7b4695701892e168a.poster.avif?t=1675471163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/8e34a285516c53d7b4695701892e168a.webm?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/8e34a285516c53d7b4695701892e168a.mp4?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你需要稳定性、记忆力，最重要的是，耐心，就像生活一样。 但你很幸运，因为你有一个强大的朋友叫“仙女”在你身边，至少可以在这段痛苦的道路上用爸爸的笑话来娱乐你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/cf9d6d0bce979cc67141487febf2e722.poster.avif?t=1675471163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/cf9d6d0bce979cc67141487febf2e722.webm?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/cf9d6d0bce979cc67141487febf2e722.mp4?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>为什么是内存？</strong><br>呃,一开始你会遇到很多陷阱,是不可避免的,所以你要记住那些陷阱是什么,那些陷阱在哪里。<br><br><strong>为什么要稳定？</strong><br>每一个动作、行为和错误都会被保存下来。 有时您可能会因为一个简单的错误而失去整个进程。 那些时光会让你尖叫，但你必须一次又一次地重新开始。 否则，你将要经历的唯一感觉就是“痛”<br><br><strong>为什么要耐心？</strong><br>如前所述，有时您可能会因为犯了一个简单的错误而失去整个来之不易的进步。 在这些时候，你应该深吸一口气，然后再继续。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/d5a3e9e853f42383d0d88c2726279c82.poster.avif?t=1675471163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/d5a3e9e853f42383d0d88c2726279c82.webm?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/d5a3e9e853f42383d0d88c2726279c82.mp4?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>怎么玩呢？</strong><br>好吧，只有两个函数：一个用于抛出 blob，一个用于拾取对象。 要抛出水滴，您必须向相反的方向拉动才能将其向前抛出。 要拾取对象，<strong><i>您必须通过按 Z</i></strong> 键来切换功能 <strong><i>。 切换它们后，您现在可以看到可拾取的对象已突出显示。 您只需单击该对象并按住它。 就是这样。 恭喜！ 你可以玩欢乐之路！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/02a7711079de219a30751b2d74ef326a.poster.avif?t=1675471163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/02a7711079de219a30751b2d74ef326a.webm?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/02a7711079de219a30751b2d74ef326a.mp4?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/797ef2b6b8d80ae3088703a5bcb6a63e.poster.avif?t=1675471163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/797ef2b6b8d80ae3088703a5bcb6a63e.webm?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300310/extras/797ef2b6b8d80ae3088703a5bcb6a63e.mp4?t=1675471163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>边玩边祝你好运！</strong></i></strong>",
